content:
Analyze this project brief: 'This is a small story for a child, around 1 page of 1000 words not more, to tell the story to a child. Give details and be nice, add some morale to the story. '.
Generate the required team structure.
Respond ONLY with a JSON matching this exact structure. Use short, unique words for 'team_name' and 'task_name' (e.g., 'Backend', 'UI', 'Database'):
{
  "managers": [
    {
      "team_name": "ShortTeamName",
      "role": "Detailed description of their role",
      "employees": [
        {"task_name": "ShortTaskName", "role": "Their specific role"}
      ]
    }
  ]
}

{
  "managers": [
    {
      "team_name": "Architect",
      "role": "Designs the story's core concept, including protagonist, setting, conflict, resolution, and the underlying moral lesson.",
      "employees": [
        {"task_name": "Blueprint", "role": "Creates a structured narrative outline detailing plot beats, character arcs, and thematic focus."}
      ]
    },
    {
      "team_name": "Scribe",
      "role": "Composes the complete narrative draft, focusing on vivid details, gentle tone, and age-appropriate engagement for children.",
      "employees": [
        {"task_name": "Inkwell", "role": "Writes the full story text, integrating sensory details and maintaining a warm, instructive voice within the target length."}
      ]
    },
    {
      "team_name": "Editor",
      "role": "Reviews and refines the draft to ensure strict adherence to the 1000-word limit, verifies moral clarity, and optimizes readability.",
      "employees": [
        {"task_name": "Proof", "role": "Edits for pacing, trims redundant sections, enhances vocabulary suitability, and performs final constraint validation."}
      ]
    }
  ]
}
